- Add `attemptElevatedInstall()` with platform-specific `elevatedInstallMacOS` / `elevatedInstallLinux`
- Add `isElevationCancelled()` ‚Äî detects user dismissing the auth dialog:
  - macOS: exit 1 + stderr contains "User canceled"
  - Linux: exit code 126
- Add `elevationCancelled?: boolean` to `CliInstallResult`
- Use `execFile` (not `exec`) with `promisify` ‚Äî paths are all app-derived, single-quote them inside shell command for safety

