### 7. Unit tests ‚Äî `packages/shared/platform/src/cli-install.test.ts`

- Non-elevated success ‚Üí no elevation attempted
- EACCES ‚Üí macOS elevation via osascript
- EACCES ‚Üí Linux elevation via pkexec
- User cancels macOS dialog ‚Üí `elevationCancelled: true`
